TITLE: Classic Action Format Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Example of a classic action format that handles user welcome functionality with manual parameter validation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/balderdashy/sails/blob/master/docs/concepts/ActionsAndControllers/ActionsAndControllers.md#2025-04-20_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
module.exports = async function welcomeUser (req, res) {
  var userId = req.param('userId');
  if (!_.isNumeric(userId)) {
    return res.badRequest(new Error('No user ID specified!'));
  }
  var user = await User.findOne({ id: userId });
  if (!user) {
    return res.redirect('/signup' );
  }
  return res.view('welcome', {name: user.name});
}
```

