SOURCE: https://github.com/balderdashy/sails/blob/master/docs/concepts/ORM/errors.md#2025-04-20_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
User.create({
  emailAddress: req.param('emailAddress')
})
.exec(function (err){
  if (err && err.code === 'E_UNIQUE') {
    return res.sendStatus(409);
  } else if (err && err.name === 'UsageError') {
    return res.badRequest();
  } else if (err) {
    return res.serverError(err);
  }

  return res.ok();
});
```

