TITLE: Testing Sails.js Routes with sails.request() Method in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to use the sails.request() method to test a Sails.js route without lifting the server to a port. It shows the setup for a Mocha test suite, including loading the Sails.js app, running a test against a GET /hotpockets route, and properly tearing down the app after tests.
