TITLE: Defining User Model with One-Way Association in Sails.js
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines a User model in Sails.js with 'name' and 'age' attributes, and a one-way association to the Pet model through the 'pony' attribute.
SOURCE: https://github.com/balderdashy/sails/blob/master/docs/concepts/ORM/Associations/OneWayAssociation.md#2025-04-20_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// myApp/api/models/User.js
module.exports = {
  attributes: {
    name: {
      type: 'string'
    },
    age: {
      type: 'number'
    },
    pony:{
      model: 'Pet'
    }
  }
}
```

